<p><a target="_blank" class="external" href="http://sinatra.github.com">Sinatra</a> and the <a target="_blank" class="external" href="http://twitter.rubyforge.org/">twitter gem</a> running on top of <a target="_blank" class="external" href="http://www.modrails.com/">Phusion Passenger</a>.</p>